data.name: label3.Text
data.value: To begin transmitting data at a 1 Hz interval to the Cansat, press BEGIN. To stop transmitting simulated pressure data to the Cansat, press STOP. The ground station shall stop transmitting data automatically when it has reached the end of the dataset.

data.name: label2.Text
data.value: To use the Cansat in simulation mode, first send the ENABLE and ACTIVATE commands. After this, press the Load Files button to load all files in the .bin directory of the project (make sure that the csv file is in the same directory as the .exe program file). Then select the simulated pressure csv file and press the Read File button. If the operation is successful, the pressure data will be read into the program.
